{
  "stem": "24130.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Once-- once we were on the train, they closed the trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were just little windows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody was trying to get some air from the windows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people were praying and crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And babies were crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some babies really got sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a little cousin, that she was named after my grandma.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Her name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Rochella. ?] And she only wanted I should hold her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was so sick, so hot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was running a fever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she had-- she-- she was so-- [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Avi, ?] hold me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Avi, ?] hold me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Give me water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Give me water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't have any water to give the sick babies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was-- we were depressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was so, so terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's crowded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were just sitting one next to the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Or, some people would stand up, so the other people could sit or lean against, sleep a little bit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then, every time the-- the train would pass by stations, they would whistle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So we-- we knew we'll be going, you know, what stations we go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came to a city, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a big city already there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the train stopped, and they opened up the doors from the train in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw the German soldiers and-- and the Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were giving them some papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the German soldiers brought water, pails of water, and put it in the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, gee, that's great.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans treat us better than the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I says, they give us at least some water for the kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I says, please.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Give me some water for the baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Give me, Rochella's so sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I gave her some water.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
